[Student "S"]
{SOUTH jumps in \Hs, showing a good suit and slam interest.

NORTH has great \H support so bids RKCB 4NT.

SOUTH responds 5\S, showing two Key Cards and the \HQ.

That is enough for NORTH to bid the slam.}

